      <section id="id1164858989040">
        <title>[LO 1.7, 2.2]</title>
        <para id="id1164859777811">Do the following on your own: </para>
        <para id="id1164859893932">a) Go to the library and find information on different types of plants that have been genetically manipulated to ensure a higher production of crops. This is an example of how technology is used for development. Write down in your own words what you understand under genetic manipulation, and what is meant by technology. Find out what happens in laboratories, and how scientists in different fields contribute to the development of a country.</para>
        <para id="id1164842706573">b) Visit the following website on the internet (you will be able to find many others):</para>
        <section id="id1164859677894">
