          <para id="id1164852042714"> Peter Rosset, Joseph Collins, Francis Moore Lappé: <emphasis effect="italics">Lessons from</emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">the Green Revolution</emphasis>, Tikkun Magazine, March/April 2000</para>
